episodes.title: Deepak Chopra in Hiding After EXTENSIVE EMAILS WITH EPSTEIN Revealed - "Cute Girls... Make Noises"!
episodes.description:
Brittany Page discusses the discovery of famous guru Deepak Chopra's extensive communications with Jeffrey Epstein, in which Chopra refers to "cute girls" and the "noises" they make, and seems totally unconcerned with litigation involving Epstein and Trump following allegations of abuse of children. Deepak Chopra has made a career out of claiming to offer people a pathway to transcendence, healing, and the divine, but his extensive communications and relationship with Epstein reveal not only his depravity and hypocrisy but also the dangers of allowing a man like this to continue to enjoy the massive platform he does.
